WEBVTT

00:04:28.452 --> 00:04:32.511
It would grow far greater
than they could ever imagine.

00:04:33.058 --> 00:04:36.114
You are a conservative member of Congress.

00:04:37.388 --> 00:04:43.402
You fear the fire of populist nationalism,

00:04:43.426 --> 00:04:46.141
because you know
that those who play with fire

00:04:46.165 --> 00:04:47.512
can't control it.

00:04:48.345 --> 00:04:50.401
You see their pitchforks and torches,

00:04:50.425 --> 00:04:53.889
and you know they're not
good building tools.

00:04:54.745 --> 00:04:59.849
The pitchforks and torches can tear down
and burn up but they can't build up.